description: Local Fort Collins SOLAR POWERED food truck! We serve up fresh eats made from scratch using quality ingredients, including organic and local sources when available! A few of our top sellers include Beer Mac n Cheese, Spring Rolls w/Peanut Sauce, Caprese Grilled Cheese, & Pulled Pork Sliders! We strive to be sustainable with our cooking and our carbon footprint, hints the solar panels on our truck! We offer plenty of vegetarian options and a few vegan choices as well! Like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter!!
name: The Sustainable Spoon
